{"tid":2321112,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"遇過D咩事差D改變你一生?","createTime":"2020-12-11T09:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T10:09:42.000Z","uid":142854,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f41d1d4e33c0a9ec84ebfd6550b865c4948dd03","tid":2321112,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"細個要去大陸探親 途中搭完飛機之後要搭多程火車<br />\n有個細路同佢阿媽坐係前排 個阿媽坐出邊 細路坐入面<br />\n由於程車有D人係好鬼遠坐過黎所以會好累<br />\n坐坐下有人趁個阿媽訓著果陣時係前排到打直咁抱走左個細路<br />\n<br />\n我果陣時被阿媽抱住 當時淨係搭左一個鐘所以仲好清醒<br />\n個細路個身形係幾秒之間就消失左<br />\n如果當時個身分調換左 開呢個post果個人就係果個細路喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91dee5efb6101a2f042f273a5f20a8b78506ba20","tid":2321112,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"但而家有人一直跟蹤你"},{"pid":"4eb1dc1edefcf205c2e66b001ec862f2d4f5a8cb","tid":2321112,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91dee5efb6101a2f042f273a5f20a8b78506ba20","tid":2321112,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"但而家有人一直跟蹤你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想擺脫佢"},{"pid":"3381ae87a166c599bc8141f064e1182bf67c0bd8","tid":2321112,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"91dee5efb6101a2f042f273a5f20a8b78506ba20","tid":2321112,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"但而家有人一直跟蹤你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:39:49.000Z","msg":"我知你係邊個架 有咩事出黎面對唔好單單打打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723c4246664dc10abd7d37d1aa33c6f17e8cbddc","tid":2321112,"uid":378177,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"我屌 細個好驚返深